{"tid":1621450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"VPN選擇","createTime":"2019-10-04T13:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:43:39.000Z","uid":130223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1191b4f9fb17d06bd7a1fd43a8f511f34c642fd","tid":1621450,"uid":130223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"今日出現某些電話公司網絡訪問LIHKG困難，難免讓人對香港政府或將通過緊急條例通過更多限制自由嘅法例。見到好多人開始搵緊VPN，幫大家推介下在國際通用嘅Proxy服務。<br />\n<br />\n某些VPN提供商或者巴打絲打有link，其實大部分係promotion，你付費佢有一個月服務使用時間獎勵或commission。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtTNZes.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtTNZes.png&h=7db1714b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOVXB1h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOVXB1h.png&h=c6f41a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/213743_0a7fc2b7d766cf88521d024ac01be30f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F213743_0a7fc2b7d766cf88521d024ac01be30f.png&h=1bff0afc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/213759_cf6fc6038cd2985c2726b42d455173b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F213759_cf6fc6038cd2985c2726b42d455173b7.png&h=bf1236b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/213818_0d7b9d00ce5c217e5088a0d16105fb85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F213818_0d7b9d00ce5c217e5088a0d16105fb85.png&h=77308d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中ProtonVPN同NordVPN速度較慢，都有3年plan嘅promotion。在內地成功登上較差。 Vyprvpn服務態度唔好，但遵守no log policy，在內地一樣大部分時間用唔到。 Astrill同ExpressVPN疑似中資公司，Astrill服務態度傲慢，Express服務響應時間短，客戶服務人員回覆快。但在內地連線效果較佳。<br />\n<br />\nPS： Astrill及ProtonVPN禁止訪問內地網站，如微博等。"}]}